metadata.name: Car Alpha #1
metadata.description: Car Alpha is a collection of unique NFTs that contemplate the perfect perspective of futuristic and vintage cars, produced freehand with paper, ink and a lot of creativity. Idealized and created by a designer with a background of more than 70 years of professional experience, who does with passion what he loves most, DESIGN. Currently around 90 years old and has worked in renowned automotive companies producing hundreds of works of art. In this collection you will find work on NFTs dating from the year 1980. Finally, take advantage of this opportunity and buy this successful model now.
